headline: What Analysts Think Drives Norfolk Southern's Shifting Outlook Amid Rail Merger Uncertainty
summary: Norfolk Southern stock has seen its consensus analyst price target edge up modestly from $307.37 to $312.53 per share, reflecting a measured shift in market outlook. This change comes as analysts weigh company execution, industry dynamics, and the anticipated effects of its proposed merger with Union Pacific.
